stories.title: New Zealand's match plan superior in 35-run win over India
stories.summary:
Virender Sehwag: lacked support from team-mates to make century count  
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
New Zealand utilised an adherence to basic disciplines to severely punish an Indian team that forget theirs to go 2-0 up with a 35-run win in the National Bank
